    <item>
      <title>2024 年香港将迎来最繁忙的 IPO 周，将有六家公司上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/six-firms-to-list-in-hong-kong-s-busiest-debut-week-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，六家公司将在香港开始交易，它们共募集资金 43.1 亿港元（5.51 亿美元），这是今年首次公开募股 (IPO) 最繁忙的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/six-firms-to-list-in-hong-kong-s-busiest-debut-week-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 02:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：法国左翼势力失利，股市抹去损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市小幅走高，因交易员们消化了法国提前大选的意外结果，该结果导致左翼集团没有足够的席位组建政府。欧元和法国债券一起下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星工会发起三天罢工，加大对员工薪酬的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/samsung-union-steps-up-pressure-over-pay-with-three-day-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，三星电子公司数千名工人举行罢工，要求提高工资，这是该韩国企业集团半个世纪历史上规模最大的劳工组织行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/samsung-union-steps-up-pressure-over-pay-with-three-day-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国大选中左翼政党意外获胜 投资者紧张不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国大选结果引发欧洲市场新一轮担忧，投资者担心左翼联盟的胜利将增加政府支出的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:26:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举结果引发财政担忧，法国股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-quoted-lower-as-left-wing-bloc-set-to-win-french-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心左翼联盟的意外胜利将导致出台对该国本已紧张的财政造成更大压力的政策，法国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-quoted-lower-as-left-wing-bloc-set-to-win-french-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 19:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
